one their skills as well. We pride ourselves on offering the most diverse and complete selection of achery items and providing the best customer service in the surrounding area.'),(1712,134,'_archery_section_content','field_5a549c786e994'),(1713,134,'archery_section_gallery','5'),(1714,134,'_archery_section_gallery','field_5a549ca59a85f'),(1715,134,'firearms_title','Firearms'),(1716,134,'_firearms_title','field_5a549d34351f4'),(1717,134,'firearms_section_banner','98'),(1718,134,'_firearms_section_banner','field_5a549d40351f5'),(1719,134,'firearms_section_content','Hunting, target practice, home protection, and self-defense are just a few reasons you may be in the market for a new firearm. If so, stop in and check out our selection! We carry rifles, shotguns, and handguns from major brands such as Remington, Winchester, Savage, Glock, Smith & Wesson, and more, all competitively prices. Don’t see what you want? Let us know! We will try our hardest to find exactly what you’re looking for. We also have a large inventory of ammunition and targets to keep you prepared and ready to go. '),(1720,134,'_firearms_section_content','field_5a549d49351f6'),(1721,134,'firearms_section_gallery','5'),(1722,134,'_firearms_section_gallery','field_5a549d52351f7'),(1723,134,'fishing_title','Fishing'),(1724,134,'_fishing_title','field_5a549e0849406'),(1725,134,'fishing_section_banner','92'),(1726,134,'_fishing_section_banner','field_5a549e1049407'),(1727,134,'fishing_section_content','A bad day of fishing is better than a good day at work. If you believe in that saying, you need to come in to All American Outdoors and check out our expansive fishing section. We have what you need to reel in the monsters, whether it be small mouth from the river, walleye at the lake, or catfish in the stream. You can pick up a new rod and reel, tackle, and all the line you could need in one stop. While you are here, be sure to tell us your best fishing story and you will hear a few in return!'),(1728,134,'